   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>(Recto);;Philinos to Zenon greeting. If you are well, it would be good. I too am well. If it is convenient to you, kindly reserve me 1,000 artabai of wheat from the new crop. And write me the price, in order that I may send it to you. Farewell.;;(Verso);;To Zenon.;(Docket, 2nd hand) Year 35, Tybi 23. Philinos about 1,000 artabai of wheat.</ab>
         </div>
